<HL>
   Economy:
   Greenspan Says Oil Prices Curb Fed Moves;
   Poll Finds Mideast Crisis Slowing Economy
   ---
   Central Bank Chief, Citing
   Inflation, Doesn't Signal
   Any Interest-Rate Cut
   ----
   By David Wessel
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/20/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
<IN>
ECONOMIC NEWS (ECO)
CDS, INTEREST RATES, COMMERCIAL PAPER (FIN)
